Chapter 1:  Introduction.

If you are reading this book, it shows that you are interested in learning
more detailed information about tournament events.  For general
information about the tournament, read the board or pick up the book
titled 'Tournament Leaflet".  This book is designed to give
detailed information on specific events.  This book will describe the
events that will take place in an arena type zone designed just for the
tournament.  See other books for pocket descriptions of other events to
take place in other areas of the Mud. 

